SUMMARY:Artist Talk & Reception with Linda Clark Johnson
DESCRIPTION:Pence Adult Art Programs\nJoin artist Linda Clark Johnson as s
 he discusses her artistic process in working with cyanotype\, including he
 r love of sunlight and her ways of gathering and arranging plants. Linda w
 ill also show visitors how to get started with cyanotype through an artist
  demo\, as well as explore her current work in her exhibit\, *Sunshine & S
 hadows*\, on view at the Pence Gallery from May 2 - June 21\, 2026.\n\nArt
 ist Talk & Reception with Linda Clark Johnson\nSunday\, May 17\, 1-2:30 PM
 \nFree Admission
